dxe5 dxe5 5. Qxd8+ Kxd8 6. f4
{ immediately striving to open lines towards the uncastled black king. Now  6...Nbd7  will take play into our next line @@StartBracket@@ see 3...Nbd7 @@EndBracket@@, but Black's most popular choice has been to pin and aim for active counterplay }
