10... O-O 11. g4
{ suddenly switching straight to direct and strong attacking mode: } 11... hxg4
12. h5 gxh5 13. f3 gxf3 14. Bxf3
{ would surely leave Black unlikely to survive down the g- and h-files after O-O-O and Rdg1. }
