4... c5 { is, once again, best met by the simple capture: } 5. dxc5 Bxc3+ 6.
bxc3 Qa5 { can be met by a manoeuvre familiar from Line B3 : } 7. Qd4 Nf6 8.
Qb4 { and here Black is under even more pressure due to the threat on g5. } *

